00:18:29.380 --> 00:18:31.380
So how much do we show?

00:18:31.380 --> 00:18:33.450
This is showing
everything that we know.

00:18:33.450 --> 00:18:36.460
It's pretty detailed,
which may not be necessary.

00:18:36.460 --> 00:18:38.430
Maybe people don't
need to see all this.

00:18:38.430 --> 00:18:40.810
So do we show
everything or we don't?

00:18:40.810 --> 00:18:43.200
Should we do an
edited-down version?

00:18:43.200 --> 00:18:47.167
Should it be super realistic, or
should it be super abstracted?

00:18:47.167 --> 00:18:48.750
That's another thing
that we're trying

00:18:48.750 --> 00:18:51.014
to figure out as
a design problem.

00:18:51.014 --> 00:18:52.430
